# Dog (Hellhound) — the "reuse" case: a new mob, zero new code. It points its
# `behaviour` at the SAME chaser archetype the zombie uses, just faster and
# weaker. Proves a mob is content: drop a .mob file, no recompile.
#
# NOTE: reuses zombie.glb as a placeholder model until a rigged dog.glb is
# authored (keep its .blend source beside it when it lands).

id              DOG
name            Hellhound
category        mob

model           zombie.glb
model_scale     0.8
model_yaw       0.0
tint            200 120 80 255
anim_walk       walk
anim_attack     attack_a
anim_death      death
anim_idle       walk

behaviour       chaser
move_speed      3.4
path_repath     0.4

health_base     90
damage          40
attack_windup   0.3
attack_range    1.3
